text: Hamilton East is an inner suburb of Newcastle, New South Wales, Australia, located west of Newcastle's central business district. ==Population== In the 2016 Census, there were 983 people in Hamilton East. 85.3% of people were born in Australia and 85.8% of people spoke only English at home. The most common responses for religion were No Religion 36.0%, Catholic 26.2% and Anglican 13.9%. ==References== Category:Suburbs of Newcastle, New South Wales
title: Hamilton East, New South Wales
